# üìù Streamlit Ace

[![GitHub][github_badge]][github_link] [![PyPI][pypi_badge]][pypi_link] 

## Installation

```sh
pip install streamlit-ace
```

## Getting started

```python
import streamlit as st

from streamlit_ace import st_ace

# Spawn a new Ace editor
content = st_ace()

# Display editor's content as you type
content
```

